title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When a directory (project) is exported and the exported jar file is placed in the same directory (project), overwriting the exported jar file for the second time leads to an out of sync message.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Save the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file with a new version.
4. Observe the out of sync message.
